nal web / reconnect\n  3. decidir si se hace **update** o **restart controlado del gateway**\n\nComo el heartbeat pide no inventar más trabajo si no toca ejecutarlo ya, dejo la alerta clara y no hago cambios todavía.\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09ca5d5822f63b080169dece0d940c8191821fc44bce7d1ee0\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":16692,"output":364,"totalTokens":70944,"cacheRead":53888,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.060662}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776209418203,"responseId":"resp_09ca5d5822f63b080169dece0cbb9c8191afce2361591769e2","__openclaw":{"id":"5beedaab","seq":24}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-14 19:05:50 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-14 19:05:54 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 19:06:54 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-14 19:07:01 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 19:08:01 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-14 19:08:04 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 19:09:04 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-14 19:09:08 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 19:10:08 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-14 19:10:10 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/Gustavo/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 — 7:15 PM (America/Bogota) / 2026-04-15 00:15 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776212108746,"__openclaw":{"id":"a9c2c81b","seq":25}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text